		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What happens when you set the TV from antenna mode to "standard cable" mode and try 95 through 99? See <a href="http://www.jneuhaus.com/fccindex/cablech.html" class="postlink">cable frequencies</a> and <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Television_channel_frequencies#Japan" class="postlink">NTSC-J frequencies</a>.

		

